        connect.
      </p>
      <div class="m-auto mt-4 flex flex-row flex-wrap gap-4">
        <IconCardLink
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/geraintguan/"
          icon="fa6-brands:linkedin"
          label="LinkedIn"
        />
        <IconCardLink
          href="https://github.com/geraintguan"
